1
00:00:29,605 --> 00:00:35,765
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

2
00:01:56,205 --> 00:01:58,605
EPISODE 28

3
00:02:01,485 --> 00:02:02,365
Sir.

4
00:02:02,845 --> 00:02:04,085
Mrs. Lan is not feeling well.

5
00:02:04,165 --> 00:02:05,445
Why don't I take you home first?

6
00:02:05,525 --> 00:02:07,125
We'll take care of Xinya.

7
00:02:07,285 --> 00:02:09,245
You must look after Xinya.

8
00:02:09,965 --> 00:02:10,805
Don't worry.

9
00:02:11,485 --> 00:02:12,565
Gu Nanxi.

10
00:02:13,005 --> 00:02:14,085
I'll leave it to you.

11
00:02:14,725 --> 00:02:15,805
Let's go.

12
00:02:21,325 --> 00:02:22,165
Xinya.

13
00:02:24,685 --> 00:02:25,725
Lanting.

14
00:02:26,725 --> 00:02:27,805
Knife.

15
00:02:27,885 --> 00:02:29,645
Do you have a knife? Do you?

16
00:02:30,565 --> 00:02:32,925
Didn't you say that if I hurt myself,

17
00:02:33,005 --> 00:02:34,725
I could keep Feng by my side?

18
00:02:35,925 --> 00:02:37,005
I'm going to hurt myself.

19
00:02:37,485 --> 00:02:39,365
-Xinya.
-I'll do whatever it takes.

20
00:02:39,445 --> 00:02:41,365
Situ Feng is not going to come back.

21
00:02:41,445 --> 00:02:44,165
Give me the knife. I beg you.

22
00:02:44,405 --> 00:02:45,645
Let me keep him by my side.

23
00:02:47,165 --> 00:02:49,365
Hua Munian, do you have a knife?

24
00:02:49,445 --> 00:02:52,325
-Give me the sleeping pills.
-Xinya, knock it off.

25
00:02:53,645 --> 00:02:55,285
Lanting.

26
00:02:57,005 --> 00:02:58,885
Please help me.

27
00:03:00,205 --> 00:03:02,685
-I beg you. Please help me.
-There's nothing you can do.

28
00:03:02,765 --> 00:03:04,565
Even if you hit your head on the wall,

29
00:03:04,645 --> 00:03:07,565
-Situ Feng wouldn't care.
-I beg you. Please help me.

30
00:03:07,965 --> 00:03:08,845
Gu Nanxi.

31
00:03:09,405 --> 00:03:11,765
Can you drag this crazy woman,
Yang Lanting, out?

32
00:03:11,845 --> 00:03:13,005
Did you call me a crazy woman?

33
00:03:14,125 --> 00:03:15,645
Did you not hear what I said?

34
00:03:16,525 --> 00:03:17,365
Look.

35
00:03:18,165 --> 00:03:21,165
You're a selfish, despicable
and reckless, crazy woman.

36
00:03:21,605 --> 00:03:22,845
You don't understand anything.

37
00:03:23,405 --> 00:03:24,565
I was only helping Xinya--

38
00:03:24,645 --> 00:03:25,605
Helping Xinya?

39
00:03:26,165 --> 00:03:27,885
Look at her right now.

40
00:03:28,165 --> 00:03:29,805
Look at what you've done to her.

41
00:03:29,885 --> 00:03:31,045
You weren't helping her.

42
00:03:32,005 --> 00:03:33,605
This was Chen Qingqing's fault.

43
00:03:33,685 --> 00:03:35,445
This has nothing to do with Chen Qingqing.

44
00:03:35,525 --> 00:03:37,245
You're the one who should be responsible.

45
00:03:37,845 --> 00:03:40,845
If you didn't plot any of those things,
Xinya wouldn't have become this way.

46
00:03:40,925 --> 00:03:43,165
Her parents wouldn't have
to worry about her every day.

47
00:03:43,245 --> 00:03:45,645
Situ Feng and Qingqing
wouldn't have had to endure that.

48
00:03:45,725 --> 00:03:47,885
Today's farce wouldn't have happened.

49
00:03:47,965 --> 00:03:49,405
All right. Stop fighting.

50
00:03:50,045 --> 00:03:51,765
Let Xinya calm down first.

51
00:03:53,045 --> 00:03:54,845
Lanting, come outside with me.

52
00:03:56,645 --> 00:03:58,165
Feng.

53
00:04:05,005 --> 00:04:06,045
Lanting.

54
00:04:06,125 --> 00:04:08,525
Weren't you going too far this time?

55
00:04:08,605 --> 00:04:13,125
You have to fight for what you truly want.

56
00:04:13,205 --> 00:04:16,204
But that doesn’t mean
that you can put a person's life at risk.

57
00:04:16,285 --> 00:04:18,845
You knew that Situ Feng
didn't like Lan Xinya.

58
00:04:18,925 --> 00:04:20,245
How could you help her?

59
00:04:22,844 --> 00:04:23,805
Gu Nanxi.

60
00:04:24,404 --> 00:04:26,165
I'm very disappointed in all of you.

61
00:04:31,245 --> 00:04:33,045
Lanting has left.

62
00:04:34,245 --> 00:04:35,845
Nobody else will help me.

63
00:04:40,885 --> 00:04:43,605
Xinya, if you want,

64
00:04:44,725 --> 00:04:46,045
I can help you.

65
00:04:49,685 --> 00:04:50,525
You?

66
00:04:53,365 --> 00:04:54,205
Xinya.

67
00:04:55,125 --> 00:04:57,645
From now on,
you have to let go of your past

68
00:04:58,165 --> 00:04:59,525
and start a new life.

69
00:05:03,085 --> 00:05:03,965
A new life?

70
00:05:05,445 --> 00:05:08,045
You can't stop thinking
about Situ Feng right now.

71
00:05:09,125 --> 00:05:10,205
But I'm telling you.

72
00:05:11,245 --> 00:05:12,445
In a few days,

73
00:05:13,405 --> 00:05:16,525
a few months or a few years,
you won't think about him anymore.

74
00:05:18,165 --> 00:05:21,325
You will meet a better man.

75
00:05:22,245 --> 00:05:25,125
Don't cry for a man who doesn't love you.

76
00:05:26,325 --> 00:05:27,805
Without Feng,

77
00:05:28,925 --> 00:05:30,245
what else can I do?

78
00:05:33,405 --> 00:05:34,525
You'll definitely meet a man

79
00:05:34,605 --> 00:05:36,805
who's better and more talented
than Situ Feng.

80
00:05:38,085 --> 00:05:41,405
He will at least be ten times
or 100 times better than him.

81
00:05:43,005 --> 00:05:45,645
Don't hurt yourself
for a man who doesn't love you.

82
00:05:48,725 --> 00:05:50,485
It won't be easy to find such a man.

83
00:05:52,805 --> 00:05:53,725
Besides,

84
00:05:55,805 --> 00:05:57,285
I'm not worthy of love.

85
00:05:57,365 --> 00:05:58,485
You are.

86
00:06:04,205 --> 00:06:05,645
Do you want to bet?

87
00:06:06,685 --> 00:06:08,165
You'll definitely find that man.

88
00:06:09,125 --> 00:06:09,965
And...

89
00:06:10,685 --> 00:06:11,845
I...

90
00:06:13,005 --> 00:06:14,405
We can look for him together.

91
00:06:22,805 --> 00:06:24,885
-Hurry, let's go.
-Let's go.

92
00:06:34,485 --> 00:06:36,205
-Qingqing.
-Yes?

93
00:06:36,285 --> 00:06:37,285
Where are we going?

94
00:06:37,365 --> 00:06:38,565
To the airport.

95
00:06:38,645 --> 00:06:40,845
I'm afraid that Lan Xinya
will create more drama.

96
00:06:40,925 --> 00:06:42,685
I'm going to hide you at my house.

97
00:06:43,365 --> 00:06:45,645
Qingqing, I'm sorry.

98
00:06:45,725 --> 00:06:47,445
I don't think I can go with you.

99
00:06:47,525 --> 00:06:48,965
-What?
-What?

100
00:06:51,405 --> 00:06:52,845
What do you mean?

101
00:06:53,605 --> 00:06:55,285
Are you going to leave me behind again?

102
00:06:55,885 --> 00:06:57,605
-Seriously?
-Seriously?

103
00:06:59,605 --> 00:07:00,445
Qingqing.

104
00:07:01,365 --> 00:07:02,525
You're silly.

105
00:07:03,365 --> 00:07:04,645
I didn't bring my ID.

106
00:07:04,725 --> 00:07:05,885
I can't get on the plane.

107
00:07:08,045 --> 00:07:08,885
That's right.

108
00:07:08,965 --> 00:07:09,805
Qingqing.

109
00:07:09,885 --> 00:07:11,085
I've promised you.

110
00:07:12,165 --> 00:07:13,965
I will never let you go.

111
00:07:14,045 --> 00:07:14,965
That's great.

112
00:07:24,725 --> 00:07:25,685
So...

113
00:07:26,125 --> 00:07:28,005
Where should we go now?

114
00:07:29,845 --> 00:07:30,965
Nowhere.

115
00:07:32,725 --> 00:07:35,365
Sometimes, when I run out of inspiration,

116
00:07:35,725 --> 00:07:39,765
I will hop on a bus
and just wander aimlessly.

117
00:07:40,525 --> 00:07:44,165
The view outside the window
will brighten up my mood.

118
00:07:44,645 --> 00:07:46,805
Then, inspiration will come to me.

119
00:07:50,365 --> 00:07:51,205
What are you doing?

120
00:07:52,605 --> 00:07:54,125
I'm writing down what you said.

121
00:07:54,485 --> 00:07:57,525
I'm making an illustration book

122
00:07:57,605 --> 00:08:00,325
of Situ Feng's best quotes

123
00:08:00,405 --> 00:08:02,125
to give back to my fans.

124
00:08:02,205 --> 00:08:04,165
It's time for me to collect materials.

125
00:08:04,245 --> 00:08:06,005
You're putting pressure on me.

126
00:08:08,405 --> 00:08:09,845
-Situ Feng.
-Yes?

127
00:08:09,925 --> 00:08:11,405
You have the right to remain silent.

128
00:08:11,485 --> 00:08:13,205
Anything you say can and will become

129
00:08:13,285 --> 00:08:16,085
Hebiancao's source materials.

130
00:09:06,205 --> 00:09:07,845
-Cheers.
-Cheers.

131
00:09:10,125 --> 00:09:13,885
Shaofang, hurry up and ask Hebiancao
if she could get me a VIP ticket.

132
00:09:13,965 --> 00:09:14,885
Hey!

133
00:09:14,965 --> 00:09:18,685
Let's make Hebiancao's boyfriend
a resident singer at my place.

134
00:09:18,765 --> 00:09:20,565
He'll sing every song that we request.

135
00:09:21,285 --> 00:09:22,125
Hold on.

136
00:09:22,685 --> 00:09:23,885
Calm down.

137
00:09:23,965 --> 00:09:27,205
Have we all just become lovesick?

138
00:09:27,685 --> 00:09:30,165
His Highness has a girlfriend.

139
00:09:30,245 --> 00:09:34,925
I think that it's wise of him
to date someone like Hebiancao.

140
00:09:35,085 --> 00:09:37,325
That's right. His Highness
has found the right girlfriend.

141
00:09:37,405 --> 00:09:38,805
He has good taste in women.

142
00:09:38,885 --> 00:09:39,925
I think that Hebiancao

143
00:09:40,005 --> 00:09:42,485
will take His Highness's career
to the next level.

144
00:09:45,565 --> 00:09:48,285
It's an honor to worship a star
with all of you.

145
00:09:48,445 --> 00:09:49,445
Cheers to our bond.

146
00:09:49,685 --> 00:09:51,765
-Cheers to our bond.
-Cheers to our bond.

147
00:09:52,725 --> 00:09:53,605
Lin Yiyang.

148
00:09:54,045 --> 00:09:55,485
Thank you for treating me to a movie.

149
00:09:55,565 --> 00:09:56,445
Don't worry about it.

150
00:10:01,965 --> 00:10:02,805
Fangfang.

151
00:10:03,805 --> 00:10:04,645
I...

152
00:10:05,245 --> 00:10:06,085
What is it?

153
00:10:07,885 --> 00:10:08,725
It's nothing.

154
00:10:13,605 --> 00:10:15,525
The movie was nice.

155
00:10:16,565 --> 00:10:17,845
Did you like the female lead?

156
00:10:20,525 --> 00:10:21,565
Yes, I liked her.

157
00:10:21,805 --> 00:10:23,685
She's pretty. Why wouldn't I like her?

158
00:10:25,765 --> 00:10:27,845
They went through so much in the movie.

159
00:10:28,165 --> 00:10:29,605
They could finally be together.

160
00:10:29,845 --> 00:10:30,685
What a nice ending.

161
00:10:39,405 --> 00:10:40,285
Hey.

162
00:11:03,925 --> 00:11:05,165
I didn't see anything.

163
00:11:05,765 --> 00:11:06,765
You're a pervert.

164
00:11:09,045 --> 00:11:10,805
Hey, I didn't see anything.

165
00:11:14,565 --> 00:11:16,125
I didn't see anything.

166
00:11:17,285 --> 00:11:18,565
I'm going back to the dorm.

167
00:11:20,965 --> 00:11:22,005
So...

168
00:11:22,125 --> 00:11:24,365
Are you going
to the library again tomorrow?

169
00:11:29,845 --> 00:11:31,405
I really didn't see anything.

170
00:11:33,085 --> 00:11:34,045
Stop talking about it.

171
00:11:49,605 --> 00:11:50,845
Guys.

172
00:11:51,645 --> 00:11:53,925
Are you both waiting
for the other person to talk first?

173
00:11:55,565 --> 00:11:57,565
Are you trying to burn my tongue?

174
00:11:59,125 --> 00:12:02,325
My little master, Situ Feng
and Madam Chen Qingqing.

175
00:12:02,405 --> 00:12:05,125
Can you give me a heads-up
before you cause trouble next time?

176
00:12:05,205 --> 00:12:06,805
The press was looking for me.

177
00:12:06,885 --> 00:12:09,445
Do you know how much money I spent
to settle this matter?

178
00:12:10,805 --> 00:12:11,685
By the way, Daniel.

179
00:12:12,605 --> 00:12:14,285
You've maxed out all these cards.

180
00:12:15,365 --> 00:12:16,805
Is there another way to pay?

181
00:12:16,885 --> 00:12:17,925
They're all maxed out?

182
00:12:18,005 --> 00:12:19,925
That's right. It's better to pay in cash.

183
00:12:20,085 --> 00:12:21,085
I've got an idea.

184
00:12:21,765 --> 00:12:23,885
I've borrowed 150,000 yuan from 9Fbank.

185
00:12:24,365 --> 00:12:25,525
Withdraw the money.

186
00:12:25,845 --> 00:12:26,685
Okay.

187
00:12:33,525 --> 00:12:34,445
Well...

188
00:12:35,445 --> 00:12:36,765
I'm sorry, Daniel.

189
00:12:36,845 --> 00:12:38,965
We'll give you a heads-up next time.

190
00:12:39,045 --> 00:12:40,365
There's no next time.

191
00:12:41,445 --> 00:12:44,925
Luckily, the fans reacted positively
to the news of you two dating.

192
00:12:45,365 --> 00:12:47,885
It seems like if you find
the right person to date,

193
00:12:48,245 --> 00:12:49,685
the fans won't overreact.

194
00:12:50,645 --> 00:12:53,925
Let me think of a way
to settle this matter.

195
00:12:54,005 --> 00:12:56,405
By the way, Situ Feng,
have you checked the chart lately?

196
00:12:56,485 --> 00:12:59,685
Your album has remained
among the top five.

197
00:13:00,805 --> 00:13:03,005
The agency thinks very highly
of you and trusts you.

198
00:13:03,085 --> 00:13:04,925
Talented boy, keep up the good work.

199
00:13:06,605 --> 00:13:07,485
But...

200
00:13:07,645 --> 00:13:08,685
Daniel.

201
00:13:08,765 --> 00:13:11,205
-Yes?
-The things between Qingqing and I

202
00:13:11,645 --> 00:13:14,365
may not be so simple.

203
00:13:15,045 --> 00:13:16,405
We've caused

204
00:13:16,485 --> 00:13:20,005
a small problem.

205
00:13:20,445 --> 00:13:22,565
Stop. Let me take a sip of water
before you tell me.

206
00:13:24,685 --> 00:13:26,685
Do you remember Qingchen?

207
00:13:27,565 --> 00:13:28,405
Yes, I do.

208
00:13:32,925 --> 00:13:36,925
Chen Qingqing? Qingchen?

209
00:13:37,165 --> 00:13:38,005
Is she Qingchen?

210
00:13:39,245 --> 00:13:40,525
It's you.

211
00:13:41,365 --> 00:13:43,085
You're also Hebiancao.

212
00:13:43,405 --> 00:13:44,805
You're quite an actress.

213
00:13:44,885 --> 00:13:47,405
Do you want to join showbiz
and help grow the film industry?

214
00:13:49,325 --> 00:13:51,605
I didn't have a choice.

215
00:13:52,085 --> 00:13:53,845
Daniel, would it be a problem

216
00:13:53,925 --> 00:13:55,165
if my fans found out

217
00:13:55,245 --> 00:13:56,525
that Chen Qingqing is Qingchen?

218
00:13:56,845 --> 00:13:58,565
But I shouldn't keep this from them.

219
00:13:58,845 --> 00:14:00,805
I'll draft a news release regarding this.

220
00:14:00,885 --> 00:14:03,005
And make the public
accept the fact step by step.

221
00:14:03,085 --> 00:14:06,805
Can you stop giving me
a challenging problem each day?

222
00:14:07,445 --> 00:14:08,285
I swear.

223
00:14:08,525 --> 00:14:10,445
This is the last problem.

224
00:14:21,005 --> 00:14:21,845
Hey!

225
00:14:22,525 --> 00:14:25,005
Isn't this Zhang Fangfang?

226
00:14:25,725 --> 00:14:28,685
I heard that you're dating Lin Yiyang.

227
00:14:30,725 --> 00:14:31,645
Where is he?

228
00:14:31,725 --> 00:14:32,965
Are you waiting for him?

229
00:14:33,685 --> 00:14:35,885
He will be here soon.
Is there anything you need from him?

230
00:14:35,965 --> 00:14:37,725
Nothing special.

231
00:14:37,805 --> 00:14:40,965
But Zhang Fangfang,
if I remember correctly,

232
00:14:41,045 --> 00:14:43,965
you came to our school
on scholarship, didn't you?

233
00:14:44,285 --> 00:14:46,805
But you're hanging out with Lin Yiyang.

234
00:14:46,885 --> 00:14:48,725
He's a bad influence.

235
00:14:49,125 --> 00:14:50,325
I'm afraid

236
00:14:50,405 --> 00:14:52,405
that you might end up getting
kicked out of school.

237
00:14:53,645 --> 00:14:56,165
Xinyan, what are you talking about?

238
00:14:56,405 --> 00:14:58,525
That will never happen to Fangfang.

239
00:14:58,765 --> 00:14:59,805
And think about it.

240
00:15:00,085 --> 00:15:01,645
If she becomes Lin Yiyang's girlfriend,

241
00:15:01,725 --> 00:15:06,005
she will be able to live a wealthy life.

242
00:15:06,525 --> 00:15:08,205
She won't have to go to school.

243
00:15:08,285 --> 00:15:12,525
However, Lin Yiyang
is just dating you for fun.

244
00:15:13,165 --> 00:15:14,005
I...

245
00:15:17,485 --> 00:15:18,725
Let's go, Fangfang.

246
00:15:22,605 --> 00:15:25,085
Lin Yiyang,
you haven't apologized to me yet.

247
00:15:26,565 --> 00:15:27,885
I'm sorry, Hong Xiaoman.

248
00:15:27,965 --> 00:15:29,205
Let me apologize to you for him.

249
00:15:29,285 --> 00:15:31,845
Why are you apologizing for him?

250
00:15:32,525 --> 00:15:34,205
Do you really think
that you're somebody to him?

251
00:15:34,285 --> 00:15:35,245
I...

252
00:15:37,645 --> 00:15:39,765
Of course she has the right
to apologize for me.

253
00:15:40,685 --> 00:15:43,205
But you don't have the right
to accept her apology.

254
00:15:43,285 --> 00:15:45,405
I heard what you said just now.

255
00:15:45,885 --> 00:15:47,165
But you were wrong about something.

256
00:15:47,245 --> 00:15:50,005
If Fangfang doesn't deserve
to attend this college,

257
00:15:50,565 --> 00:15:53,045
I'm sure that the two of you
would get expelled sooner than her.

258
00:15:53,125 --> 00:15:54,765
How dare you bully us?

259
00:15:54,845 --> 00:15:56,885
Aren't you afraid
of getting kicked out of college?

260
00:15:57,205 --> 00:15:58,965
Did anyone see you getting bullied by me?

261
00:16:00,525 --> 00:16:01,925
But something came to my mind

262
00:16:02,525 --> 00:16:03,565
after seeing you two.

263
00:16:03,645 --> 00:16:05,965
I have a very special hobby lately.

264
00:16:06,045 --> 00:16:07,205
Isn't that right, Fangfang?

265
00:16:08,845 --> 00:16:09,685
Yes.

266
00:16:11,125 --> 00:16:11,965
Lately,

267
00:16:12,445 --> 00:16:14,285
I like to raise scorpions.

268
00:16:15,125 --> 00:16:18,165
A scorpion loves to sting a girl's lips.

269
00:16:19,085 --> 00:16:21,205
If you don't leave Fangfang alone,

