301
00:19:00,685 --> 00:19:01,805
Right?

302
00:19:02,725 --> 00:19:03,885
Look at me.

303
00:19:04,405 --> 00:19:08,005
Look at these pair of glasses,
these freckles and this hair.

304
00:19:10,285 --> 00:19:11,165
Come to think of it.

305
00:19:11,365 --> 00:19:12,365
I look

306
00:19:12,445 --> 00:19:15,125
like a combination of SpongeBob and Arale.

307
00:19:15,205 --> 00:19:16,045
Do you think so?

308
00:19:16,285 --> 00:19:17,125
Look.

309
00:19:18,805 --> 00:19:20,285
"Look, Patrick Star.

310
00:19:20,445 --> 00:19:23,965
A cloud has appeared in the clear sky."

311
00:19:25,365 --> 00:19:28,005
"That cloud is really a cloud."

312
00:19:33,085 --> 00:19:35,525
Besides, I'm doing this

313
00:19:35,605 --> 00:19:38,685
