and Lu Jingyang will catch me.

314
00:19:38,765 --> 00:19:42,765
Therefore, I have to act like Spider-Man.

315
00:19:42,845 --> 00:19:45,685
This is my mask.

316
00:19:45,765 --> 00:19:48,525
But you don't have to be afraid anymore.
You don't need the makeup now.

317
00:19:49,445 --> 00:19:50,325
You're right.

318
00:19:52,165 --> 00:19:53,725
