320
00:19:55,885 --> 00:19:57,165
and see how everyone will react?

321
00:19:58,965 --> 00:19:59,925
Really?

322
00:20:00,605 --> 00:20:02,645
But I'm used to this look.

323
00:20:02,965 --> 00:20:06,285
If I become pretty all of a sudden,
I will be making a counterattack.

324
00:20:07,285 --> 00:20:09,365
-You will become the campus beauty.
-Really?

325
00:20:09,445 --> 00:20:11,125
The Goddess will become a joke.

326
00:20:13,125 --> 00:20:16,805
They've always been a joke in my eyes

327
00:20:16,885 --> 00:20:19,285
The biggest joke ever

328
00:20:24,165 --> 00:20:25,125
Chen Qingqing?

329
00:20:40,405 --> 00:20:42,165
She's so pretty.

330
00:20:42,245 --> 00:20:43,885
Isn't she Qingchen?

331
00:20:43,965 --> 00:20:45,485
I can't stop drooling over her.

332
00:20:48,725 --> 00:20:50,045
She's so pretty.

333
00:20:54,325 --> 00:20:55,685
There are two good-looking people

334
00:20:55,805 --> 00:20:58,325
in the class.

335
00:20:58,525 --> 00:21:00,085
You must feel really lucky.

336
00:21:00,165 --> 00:21:01,125
That's right.

337
00:21:01,485 --> 00:21:02,845
Zhang Fangfang is also very pretty.

338
00:21:02,925 --> 00:21:04,245
We're really lucky.

339
00:21:04,325 --> 00:21:06,205
That's right. We're aware

340
00:21:06,285 --> 00:21:08,085
that we'll never get
to date girls like them.

341
00:21:08,165 --> 00:21:10,845
Therefore, I'm happy
to just be able to look at them.

342
00:21:11,325 --> 00:21:12,365
That’s true.

343
00:21:13,165 --> 00:21:15,645
-Chen Qingqing is so beautiful.
-Chen Qingqing is so beautiful.

344
00:21:21,285 --> 00:21:23,365
Please don't go away.

345
00:21:24,925 --> 00:21:26,485
-So pretty.
-So pretty.

346
00:21:31,205 --> 00:21:32,045
Situ Feng.

347
00:21:33,165 --> 00:21:37,325
Do you notice anything different
about me today?

348
00:21:39,645 --> 00:21:40,485
No, I don't.

349
00:21:40,845 --> 00:21:42,245
You didn't wear your glasses.

350
00:21:42,365 --> 00:21:45,285
Even if you walk on the streets like this,
no one will take a glance at you.

351
00:21:52,405 --> 00:21:53,645
What are you looking at?

352
00:21:53,725 --> 00:21:55,365
Don't you need to study?

353
00:21:56,725 --> 00:21:58,565
You only care about your appearances.

354
00:21:58,725 --> 00:22:00,365
You should be embarrassed of yourselves.

355
00:22:01,085 --> 00:22:03,605
Have you solved the permutations
and combinations on the blackboard?

356
00:22:07,685 --> 00:22:08,565
Turn around.

357
00:22:10,325 --> 00:22:11,445
-Chen Qingqing.
-Yes?

358
00:22:11,525 --> 00:22:12,365
Teach me.

359
00:22:13,725 --> 00:22:16,085
But Your Highness,
this is the Chemistry textbook.

360
00:22:18,525 --> 00:22:21,125
Are permutations
and combinations not Chemistry?

361
00:22:22,965 --> 00:22:23,845
Yes.

362
00:22:25,125 --> 00:22:26,405
You're close.

363
00:22:38,525 --> 00:22:39,365
Nanxi.

364
00:22:44,725 --> 00:22:46,165
Over there.

365
00:22:46,245 --> 00:22:48,245
Right there.

366
00:22:56,005 --> 00:22:57,165
Who's looking at you?

367
00:22:57,245 --> 00:22:59,205
Why were you trying
to act cool all of a sudden?

368
00:22:59,525 --> 00:23:00,645
