371
00:23:04,285 --> 00:23:05,685
Where?

372
00:23:05,765 --> 00:23:08,805
Ten o'clock.

373
00:23:14,725 --> 00:23:16,805
Hello. So you've found out
where I go to school.

374
00:23:16,885 --> 00:23:18,365
Situ Feng, are you a student here too?

375
00:23:18,445 --> 00:23:21,045
That's right. Do you want my autograph
or do you want to take a photo with me?

376
00:23:21,125 --> 00:23:23,285
We're looking
for the famous Chen Qingqing.

377
00:23:23,845 --> 00:23:26,125
We heard that she goes to this school.
She's a wealthy girl,

378
00:23:26,205 --> 00:23:27,765
but she chose to live like a commoner.

379
00:23:27,845 --> 00:23:28,885
We're really inspired by her.

380
00:23:28,965 --> 00:23:31,205
Can you give her
these flowers and letters?

381
00:23:32,325 --> 00:23:33,365
-Thank you.
-Thank you.

382
00:23:33,845 --> 00:23:34,685
-Okay.
-Thank you.

383
00:23:37,885 --> 00:23:38,805
Thank you.

384
00:23:40,845 --> 00:23:44,205
Actually, I can give you my autograph.

385
00:23:45,165 --> 00:23:46,005
Well,

386
00:23:46,085 --> 00:23:49,165
I went to your signing event once.
I've already got your autograph.

387
00:23:49,245 --> 00:23:51,085
But thank you.

388
00:24:08,165 --> 00:24:10,285
Can you tell us the progress
of your latest comic book?

389
00:24:10,405 --> 00:24:12,085
Hey!

390
00:24:12,165 --> 00:24:13,965
-Show me the characters.
-Move.

391
00:24:14,685 --> 00:24:16,525
Hey, what are you doing?

392
00:24:16,605 --> 00:24:18,805
She's pretty, but it doesn't mean
that you can harass her.

393
00:24:18,885 --> 00:24:21,445
Also, stop giving her gifts.

394
00:24:21,525 --> 00:24:23,525
Can you not be so shallow?

395
00:24:23,605 --> 00:24:26,885
We represent
the Ballet Academy of Yuncheng.

396
00:24:26,965 --> 00:24:31,125
Miss Chen Qingqing's ballet technique
has reached the realm of the fairies.

397
00:24:31,205 --> 00:24:33,765
We really hope to witness
your performance.

398
00:24:33,845 --> 00:24:34,925
Thank you.

399
00:24:35,005 --> 00:24:36,805
We're from the Comics Club.

400
00:24:36,885 --> 00:24:41,325
Goddess Chen Qingqing's drawings remind me
of several pioneer cartoonists from Japan.

401
00:24:41,405 --> 00:24:43,605
I hope to directly learn from her.

402
00:24:44,245 --> 00:24:45,525
We're from the Piano Association.

403
00:24:45,605 --> 00:24:48,725
Miss Chen Qingqing's music
has cleansed our souls.

404
00:24:48,805 --> 00:24:51,965
Just the thought of it
makes me want to cry.

405
00:24:55,405 --> 00:24:57,205
You're exaggerating.

406
00:24:57,285 --> 00:24:58,125
It's true.

407
00:24:58,205 --> 00:25:00,325
After seeing the video
of Goddess Chen Qingqing,

408
00:25:00,405 --> 00:25:01,245
we were all shocked.

409
00:25:01,325 --> 00:25:03,245
And it's unbelievable
that she's also so pretty.

410
00:25:03,325 --> 00:25:05,765
I'm no match for her.

411
00:25:08,925 --> 00:25:12,685
After hearing your confession,

412
00:25:14,805 --> 00:25:15,805
I'm pretty shocked too.

413
00:25:16,365 --> 00:25:20,325
Mister, please don't block our way.
We're trying to learn from our goddess.

414
00:25:26,925 --> 00:25:27,965
Thank you.

415
00:25:30,405 --> 00:25:31,405
Excuse me.

416
00:25:33,285 --> 00:25:34,325
Goddess.

417
00:25:34,405 --> 00:25:35,365
Thank you.

418
00:25:35,925 --> 00:25:39,125
-Miss Chen Qingqing, I worship you.
-Goddess Qingqing, you're amazing.

419
00:25:47,805 --> 00:25:49,965
Hello, Daniel.
Qingqing's gone back to being pretty.

420
00:25:50,045 --> 00:25:51,165
Aren't you going to step in?

421
00:25:51,245 --> 00:25:52,925
Gosh. You've never asked me

422
00:25:53,005 --> 00:25:54,845
to step into anything
since you made your debut.

423
00:25:54,925 --> 00:25:55,805
I...

424
00:25:55,965 --> 00:25:57,925
I'm doing this for her.

425
00:25:58,005 --> 00:25:58,845
Think about it.

426
00:25:58,925 --> 00:26:02,125
Once her looks are exposed,
she will get caught up in scandals.

427
00:26:02,365 --> 00:26:04,685
