430
00:26:08,805 --> 00:26:12,845
Gosh, Situ Feng.

431
00:26:13,005 --> 00:26:14,165
Give me some advice.

432
00:26:14,245 --> 00:26:16,125
You don't understand the public at all.

433
00:26:16,565 --> 00:26:18,365
The frog became a prince.

434
00:26:18,645 --> 00:26:20,005
The beast also became a prince.

435
00:26:20,085 --> 00:26:22,405
The prince and princess
lived happily ever after.

436
00:26:26,005 --> 00:26:28,085
