They didn't.

437
00:26:28,165 --> 00:26:30,805
The public will be thrilled
to see an ugly girl become pretty.

438
00:26:30,885 --> 00:26:32,765
There won't be any negative coverage.

439
00:26:33,045 --> 00:26:35,085
I think the public
will like Chen Qingqing.

440
00:26:35,165 --> 00:26:36,325
You know what?

441
00:26:36,405 --> 00:26:37,765
